title: Breaking: Baek Yerin Reportedly Dating Fellow Singer Cloud
text:
What a musically talented couple! 
According to a local news outlet, singer Baek Yerin is dating producer and singer Cloud (real name Go Hyung Suk). They have reportedly been dating for months, after working together as colleagues and developing feelings for each other. 
Baek Yerin met Cloud during preparations for her first solo album, “Frank,” that was released in November 2015. He arranged all the songs in the album and also contributed as a composer and lyricist. Cloud also participated in Baek Yerin’s digital single “Bye Bye My Blue,” and in the album, there is a song called “Her/His Sea,” and “sea” is allegedly Cloud’s affectionate nickname for Baek Yerin. 
Baek Yerin is 19 years old in Korean reckoning and debuted as part of JYP Entertainment’s female duo, 15&. Cloud is 25 years old and he debuted as the keyboardist for the band Bye Bye Band Man. He recently embarked on a solo career and will be holding a solo showcase on March 19 in Seoul. 
Either sides have yet to confirm the relationship. Stayed tuned to Soompi for updates!
